another stunning
revelation.

00:11.011 --> 00:16.983 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The New York Times reports that
President
Trump asked James Comey directly
to shut down

00:17.017 --> 00:20.186 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
