by the former
FBI director.

00:23.056 --> 00:24.924 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Then:

00:24.958 --> 00:27.727 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
H.R. MCMASTER, U.S. National
Security Adviser:
The president wasn't even aware
of where this

00:27.761 --> 00:29.162 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
