or method
of the information either.

00:31.965 --> 00:34.501 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Shooting from the
hip.

00:34.534 --> 00:38.738 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
President Trump's reported
disclosure of sensitive
intelligence to Russian
diplomats in the Oval

00:38.772 --> 00:44.978 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Office sparks a firestorm of
questions and
calls by lawmakers for a full
transcript of

00:45.011 --> 00:46.780 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
