00:46.813 --> 00:50.750 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Plus: Amid growing tensions,
Turkey's leader
visits the White House after
clashing over

00:50.784 --> 00:54.521 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
