states are trying to protect
millions of students

01:00.460 --> 01:02.395 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
on their rides every day.

01:02.429 --> 01:04.197 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MARK ROSEKIND, Former
Administrator, National
Highway Traffic Safety
Administration: Three-point

01:04.230 --> 01:08.301 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
