05:56.956 --> 06:00.993 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: National
Security Adviser
H.R. McMaster used that phrase,
"wholly appropriate,"

06:01.027 --> 06:06.165 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
