last week.

06:09.469 --> 06:14.040 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The storm began Monday evening,
first in The
Washington Post, and quickly
followed by other

06:14.073 --> 06:16.275 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
