information given
to the U.S. by an ally in the
Middle East,

06:26.753 --> 06:29.322 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
but without that ally's
permission.

06:29.355 --> 06:35.695 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
