plot based
in Syria that involved laptops
on airplanes.

06:35.728 --> 06:40.166 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The New York Times reported
today that Israel
was the source of that
information, though

06:40.199 --> 06:42.034 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
