confirm it.

06:42.068 --> 06:46.005 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
QUESTION: Mr. President, did you
share classified
intelligence information with
the Russians?

06:46.038 --> 06:50.343 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: The president
himself ignored
questions today as he met with
Turkey's president,

06:50.376 --> 06:52.712 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
