06:54.614 --> 06:56.783 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP, President of the
United States:
Well, we had a very, very
successful meeting

06:56.816 --> 06:59.919 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
with the foreign minister of
Russia.

06:59.952 --> 07:04.857 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Our fight is against ISIS, as
General McMaster
said.

07:04.891 --> 07:08.861 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we want to get as many to
help fight terrorism
as possible.

07:08.895 --> 07:12.932 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: That followed
a series of
tweets this morning, saying: "As
president,

07:12.965 --> 07:17.937 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
