07:45.198 --> 07:47.500 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: But none of
the news accounts
had alleged that the president
revealed sources

07:47.533 --> 07:49.735 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
