he did elaborate
just a bit.

08:02.548 --> 08:06.519 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
H.R. MCMASTER: That the
president wasn't even
aware of where this information
came from.

08:06.552 --> 08:09.922 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He wasn't briefed on the source
or method
of the information either.

08:09.956 --> 08:14.527 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: In Moscow,
Kremlin spokesman
Dmitry Peskov dismissed the
story.

08:14.560 --> 08:18.030 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DMITRY PESKOV, Spokesman for
Vladimir Putin
(through translator): It's
complete nonsense,

08:18.064 --> 08:20.066 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
