confirmed.

08:20.099 --> 08:25.104 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: But the
episode raised fears
about how U.S. allies might
react.

08:25.137 --> 08:29.909 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
One European official told the
Associated
Press that his country may stop
sharing intelligence

08:29.942 --> 08:31.811 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
with Washington.

08:31.844 --> 08:36.148 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The revelations also rippled
through Congress,
on the heels of the president's
firing of

08:36.182 --> 08:38.951 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
