record of the
Oval Office meeting with the
Russian diplomats.

09:08.347 --> 09:10.283 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

09:10.316 --> 09:14.287 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
