can handle
our nations most closely kept
secrets.

09:27.967 --> 09:32.672 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: With the White
House in
damage control mode, CIA
Director Mike Pompeo

09:32.705 --> 09:36.309 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
