someone outside
of those of us that are cleared
with the security,

14:35.140 --> 14:37.977 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and that's the president of the
United States.

14:38.010 --> 14:41.780 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If, indeed, it was on the
subject that -- and
